title: I AM ATHLETE | KAMARU USMAN: I Learned More From My One Loss Than My Wins
description:
SUBSCRIBE ➡️ https://www.youtube.com/c/IAMATHLETE?sub_confirmation=1
WATCH MORE ➡️ https://www.youtube.com/c/IAMATHLETE

Nigerian-American professional mixed martial artist and current,  Kamarudeen Usmanm Joins Brandon Marshall, Adam "Pacman" Jones, LeSean "Shady" McCoy, and D.J. Williams in episode 45 of I Am Athlete. Watch and listen as the current UFC Welterweight Champion walks us through his UFC Career journey as well as his preparation for his upcoming rematch vs Leon Edwards on August 20, 2022 at UFC 278 for the UFC Welterweight Championship in Salt Lake City, Utah.

KAMARU USMAN VS LEON EDWARDS
AUGUST 20th, 2022 at UFC 278 on PPV
UFC WORLD WELTERWEIGHT CHAMPIONSHIP
